# Custom Components

TaskHub includes several custom components for common UI patterns.

## CustomLoader

A custom loading indicator with the following features:

- Purple background matching the app's theme
- Custom text with default "Please wait..."
- Optional cancel button
- Semi-transparent overlay
- Rotating animation for the loader icon

```dart
// Basic usage
CustomLoaderWithAnimation.show(context);

// With custom text
CustomLoaderWithAnimation.show(
  context,
  text: 'Loading data...',
);

// With cancel button
CustomLoaderWithAnimation.show(
  context,
  text: 'Uploading file...',
  showCancelButton: true,
  onCancel: () {
    Navigator.of(context).pop();
    // Handle cancel action
  },
);

// Hide the loader
CustomLoaderWithAnimation.hide(context);
```

The loader displays as a modal dialog with a dark overlay to prevent interaction with the underlying UI. The animation provides visual feedback that a process is ongoing.

Location: `lib/widgets/custom_loader.dart`

